Author: FMT_Austin
Title: [ANN] [COINSALE] | FREE MARKET TOKEN | PRESALE ON NOW
Body: We have been extremely busy working on the project as opposed to just Shilling  Here are some of the key achievements the team have made in the last couple months;  -          Launched a working buy/sell platform to market we and are merely weeks away from 'Version 2' of the platform -          Captured the attention and support of NEM Foundation; who are providing global support to the project. -          Signed a deal with an Augmented Reality Game to exclusively integrate FMT though gameplay and compliment the Ecryptosore.com user experience, providing significant Merchant exposure and marketing reach. -          Locked in a deal with Logicbase Interactive and the student guild for one of the top 50 Universities (Globally) to include FMT wallet and AR game into the Uni app with an active user-base of 15,000 students. -          Recently the team secured an agreement with Ainslie Bullion to provide merchants with a fast and secure option for liquidity from crypto (Bitcoin, Ethereum, Ripple, Bitcoin Cash and Litecoin) to either Fait, gold or Silver. -          Secured an agreement with Ainslie Bullion to allow liquidity for platform users directly into Fiat/Gold/silver. -          Listed millions of dollars of property and community land-shares -          Facilitated the transaction of the first land-share sale (in BTC and ETH) worth over AUD$150,000. Major sponsor of the upcoming Crypto Austrlia, Crypto for Blokes and Crypto for Chics meet up in Melbourne on 12th July Media Party with NEM scheduled for 13th July (Melbourne) In talks with exchanges    We have had a number of press releases go out about including:  https://stockhead.com.au/tech/ecryptosale-is-the-ebay-of-cryptocurrency-and-its-looking-to-raise-12m/  http://www.australianpropertyjournal.com.au/  (front page article - Access via a paid subscription)  https://www.investin[Suspicious link removed]/ecryptostore-community-land-development/  https://buff.ly/2IVJIYf (Yahoo finance)  We also had a another interview released:  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gbBGpm1eNH0&t=2s (A Crypto Current Affair)  We have several really exciting developments in the press releases  Join the telegram T.me/FMTofficial for more updates and the latest press releases   The FMT token layer is being built on the NEM blockchain to deliver a suite of token functionality for Ecryptostore.com and the Augmented Reality game.  NEM’s fast transaction times, enterprise grade blockchain that can handle around 4,000 T/s with Mijin and Catapult, delivers a seamless user experience which is critical for ecommerce.  NEM’s Blockchain also allows FMT (a Token Mosaic) to be customised to suit the ecosystem it was designed for, to be interoperable across multiple platforms.

Title: [ANN] [COINSALE] | FREE MARKET TOKEN | PRESALE ON NOW
Body: The project provides us with a platform for electronic money transactions with low fees and a maximum of 15% deductible transaction fees for charity organizations on a monthly basis. I really see the project moving towards community service. The project reads "Available deals in electronic and fiat money". Is platform able to exchange for both cash?

Author: brookearthur
Title: [ANN] [COINSALE] | FREE MARKET TOKEN | PRESALE ON NOW
Body: We have a functioning platform that uses both crypto and fiat and our token escrow system protects merchants from market volatility.

Author: brookearthur
Title: [ANN] [COINSALE] | FREE MARKET TOKEN | PRESALE ON NOW
Body: Merchants receive crypto or fiat, depending what the buyer purchases in. For the easy onramp to crypto buyers can purchase FMT tokens and use to buy good. Or buyers can connect other crypto wallets and use their chosen cryptocurrency.

Author: Jobbernowl
Title: [ANN] [COINSALE] | FREE MARKET TOKEN | PRESALE ON NOW
Body: Do you realize how your title sounds for investors - "Free Market Token"? (not very promising) And if I understand correctly the main advantage compared to Amazon/Ebay is a much lower service fee?  Do you have any really new feature? And what is the purpose of blockchain - to serve as an internal payment system, like Paypal on Ebay?

Author: Bziir
Title: [ANN] [COINSALE] | FREE MARKET TOKEN | PRESALE ON NOW
Body: The Free Market Token has a mission of becoming the number one selling and buying platform of cryptocurrency in the world by using an Ecrystore system that allows users to make sales, purchases and review services globally.
